Package com.ibm.ccl.soa.core.saf.ui.handler

SAF UI Handlers for UI related tasks.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IInterfaceUIHandler This interface must be implemented by all interface ui handlers.
IInterfaceUIHandler.IInterfaceDescriptionProvider The IInterfaceUIHandler.IInterfaceDescriptionProvider maps an interface object to an optional image and optional text string used to display the element in the viewer's control.
IUIHandler This class provides a common interface for all ui handlers contributed to the framework.
 

Class Summary
AbstractInterfaceUIHandler This class is to be extended by all interface UI handler contributions.
AbstractUIHandler This class provides common convenient methods for handler implementations.
